item.title: CVE-2022-1953|2024-08-03T00:24:42.631Z -- unknown -- product%20configurator%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Product Configurator for WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 1.2.32 suffers from an arbitrary file deletion vulnerability via an AJAX action, accessible to unauthenticated users, which accepts user input that is being used in a path and passed to unlink() without validation first
